description: Welcome to the most coveted block in South Boston, where the vibrant pulse of city life awaits just outside your door. Enjoy exquisite dining, lush parks, and effortless public transportation access. Established in 2018, 14 W Broadway epitomizes full-service living, featuring exceptional amenities like a dedicated concierge, a state-of-the-art fitness center, and a breathtaking rooftop deck offering panoramic views of the city and water. The sought-after 2 bedroom/ 2 bathroom floor plan showcases bedrooms thoughtfully positioned on opposite sides, creating a spacious and inviting atmosphere. Expansive floor-to-ceiling windows flood the interiors with natural light, enhancing warmth. The open kitchen and dining area, equipped with premium Wolf and Sub-Zero appliances, are perfect for entertaining. Additional building amenities include a stylish club room and a convenient dog washing station. This residence truly embodies modern luxury living in South Boston.
